<section id="about">
  <!-- Optional: add a profile picture -->
  <!-- <img src="profile.jpg" alt="Tibo Duran" class="profile-pic"> -->
  <h1>Tibo Duran</h1>
  <div class="subtitle">Assistant Professor in AI/Machine learning and Molecular modeling</div>
  <p>
    I am a faculty member in the Department of Microbiology and Plant Pathology.
    
  </p>
  <p>
    My research integrates artificial intelligence, machine learning (AI/ML), 
    and nano-scale molecular modeling to investigate disease mechanisms and advance bioinformatics analyses. 
    By combining computational modeling with large-scale biological data, 
    my work aims to improve disease prediction, classification, and therapeutic discovery and delivery.
  </p>
</section>

<section id="research">
  <h2>Research</h2>
  <ul>
    
    <li>Using AI and machine learning for disease modeling in both agriculture and human health</li>
    <li>Computational modeling and molecular dynamics (MD) simulations of complex biological systems</li>
    <li>Biopharmaceutical, pharmaceutical engineering, agriculture and plant applications</li>
    <li>Multiscale modeling and simulations</li>
  </ul>
</section>

